# Marketcheck API key – required for the live profit feature on vehicle cards.
# Sign up / retrieve your key at: https://www.marketcheck.com/marketcheck-apis/pricing/
# Free tier: 100 requests / day.
#
# Copy this file to .env.local and replace the placeholder with your real key.
# .env.local is git-ignored and must never be committed.
VITE_MARKETCHECK_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
